token_info.name: Adventure's of Túlio & Tiba #3
token_info.description: CHAOS! In the last episode "Douglas, the Demon" bit Túlio's foot, who left his shoe behind to get away. Now the terrible giant babies are fascinated by the bad odor that the foot gives off. Túlio is very sad. "Adventure's of Túlio & Tiba" is my new series, produced in VR. Gravity Sketch + Blender. WiW (May 7, 2021).
